{"tid":551351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局長: 小學已預留5至6月考BCA","createTime":"2018-02-05T14:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T06:45:12.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"feb60b00074c501819cf55b246b30efa22938f28","tid":551351,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/223358_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F223358_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9bfd2ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局局長楊潤雄出席新春傳媒午宴時表示，目前BCA檢討委員會的工作仍在進行，目前學校已預留5至6月考BCA，局方最遲於3月內公佈今年是否續推BCA及推行形式。<br />\n<br />\nBCA委員會原定去年12月提交報告，但楊潤雄今指委員會須預留多些時間收集不同持份者的意見。他形容BCA議題在社會上富爭議，「真係要好小心處理」。當局方收到委員會的建議後，會合理平衡專業考慮和社會意見下最後決定。至於BCA會否以自願性質或抽樣形式推行，楊指未有既定方案。<br />\n<br />\n楊被問到，若果續推BCA如何說服家長接受，楊稱家長反應也是局方考慮因素之一，但坦言局方決定「好難滿足所有人訴求」，「希望大家心平氣和」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180205/57795108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F57795108&d=efTyPGwSmWvSIciG6hPrPf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9d627676\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180205%2F57795108&h=b07af17b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180205/57795108</a>"},{"pid":"209665c14197b25be72b074cb62ad48c7e13fd88","tid":551351,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T06:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392cead63fe965a9c0bbb81061cdf9a26afdb1c8","tid":551351,"uid":16178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-08T06:45:12.000Z","msg":"以前唔係叫tsa?幾時又改番做bca"}]}